**Starting your SIP earlier** — even by a few years — has a dramatic impact on final wealth due to compounding. A 5-year delay in starting a ₹10,000/month SIP at 12% can cost you over ₹1 crore in final corpus. This calculator quantifies the exact opportunity cost of delay.
